e=1> Actually Corpsed I think they are very related, they both are based on TRUST and AGREEMENT.  In both cases the parties had come to a mutual Agreement, and trusted that the other party would hold their hand of the bargain.<br>
<br>
Just like in RL, your word (at least for most people) is one of your most precious asset.  If people can't trust you to follow what you say you would do than you wont deal with those people on any level.<br>
<br>
Would you tank in a group where the cleric says they would heal but don't !! No you wouldnt !!   Would you group with a wiz that is suppose to evac but gates when shit hits the fan !! No you wouldnt !! <br>
<br>
It is all a question of trust and agreement between people (even if often the agreement is implied such as in a cleric in a group, or a wiz to evac).<br>
